1. Ja *pokušavam* da shvatim tvoje razloge. (I am *trying* to understand your reasons.)
2. Ti *pokušavaš* da me ubediš da je to loša ideja. (You are *trying* to convince me that it's a bad idea.)
3. Ona *pokušava* da se seti svog detinjstva. (She is *trying* to remember her childhood.)
4. Mi *pokušavamo* da izbegnemo konflikt sa njima. (We are *trying* to avoid a conflict with them.)
5. Vi *pokušavate* da pronađete najbolje rešenje za ovaj problem. (You are *trying* to find the best solution for this problem.)
6. Oni *pokušavaju* da se dogovore oko rasporeda. (They are *trying* to agree on the schedule.)
7. Kada *pokušam* da zaspim, uvek mi pada na pamet taj problem. (When I *try* to fall asleep, that problem always comes to mind.)
8. Ne *pokušavaj* da me ubediš da je to istina. (Don't *try* to convince me that it's true.)
9. *Pokušavajući* da se snađem u novom gradu, slučajno sam zalutao. (While *trying* to get around in a new city, I accidentally got lost.)
10. Nisam siguran da li će uspeti, ali *pokušaću* da dobijem taj posao. (I'm not sure if I'll succeed, but I will *try* to get that job.)